videos.description: Jalen Hurts puts Alabama in scoring position after big gain.
videos.headline: Jalen Hurts escapes the pocket for a 29-yard gain

videos.description: Bo Scarbrough breaks through a defender to get into the end zone from six yards out.
videos.headline: Scarbrough puts the Tide on the board

videos.description: Jordan Wilkins shows off athleticism hurdling over the Alabama defense.
videos.headline: Wilkins goes up and over an Alabama defender

videos.description: Jalen Hurts finds Hale Hentges wide open in the end zone to extend the Alabama lead.
videos.headline: Jalen Hurts finds Hentges for the 3-yard TD

videos.description: Jalen Hurts finds a wide open Josh Jacobs for the 18-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jalen Hurts picks up his 2nd TD with pass to Jacobs

videos.description: Jalen Hurts accounts for his third touchdown with a 10-yard score.
videos.headline: Jalen Hurts breaks away from a tackler for the score

videos.description: Nick Saban talks with Holly Rowe after a big halftime lead over Ole Miss.
videos.headline: Saban shares halftime thoughts on Jalen Hurts

videos.description: Najee Harris easily scores for the Crimson Tide as they add onto their lead.
videos.headline: Harris walks in for the 4-yard TD

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa replaces Jalen Hurts and gets into the end zone from two yards out.
videos.headline: Tagovailoa continues the rout for Alabama

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa finds Henry Ruggs III for the eight-yard touchdown,
videos.headline: Ruggs adds on for the Tide

videos.description: Ronnie Clark celebrates with his teammates after scoring his first career touchdown at Alabama.
videos.headline: Clark scores first career TD

videos.description: Nick Saban and the Crimson Tide defeat Ole Miss but look to improve down the road.
videos.headline: Saban proud of team after win

videos.description: Jalen Hurts accounts for three touchdowns as Alabama defeats Ole Miss.
videos.headline: Jalen Hurts leads Alabama to decisive victory
